  |   Kyota: Nozomi Chikamura, Jin: Ryosuke Sakamaki, Maria: Maria          |
  |   Naganawa.                                                             |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Blade: Yui Ishikawa.                                                  |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Rebellio: Ryota Yoshizaki, Stella: Ryoko Shiraishi, Crimm: Suguru     |
  |   Narisawa.                                                             |
  |                                                                         |
  |   Isola: Miku Ito, Bakto: Atsushi Tanaka, Dystnine: Yuichiro Umehara.   |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Fast-paced, stylish 2D action eXplodes onto the scene               |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Acquire EX Weapons from bosses for eXtreme firepower                |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Utilize a wide variety of abilities that allow players of all       |
  |     skill levels to eXcel                                               |
  |                                                                         |
  |   * Experience the story of people surviving in a world where they      |
  |     are on the brink of eXtermination                                   |
